## Usage

Install the plugin:

```bash
npm i vite-plugin-ai-mock -D
```

Configure in `vite.config.ts`:

```ts
import { aiMockPlugin } from "vite-plugin-ai-mock";

export default {
  plugins: [
    aiMockPlugin({
      dataDir: "mock/ai",
      endpoint: "/api/ai/mock",
    }),
  ],
};
```
